** Popcorn At the Pops Columbus Symphony Orchestra
------------------------------------------------------------

July 18th

Music in the air, grass under your feet and lots of fun activities anchor these fun-filled family events. Bring your family and your picnic basket for an evening to remember at the Columbus Bicentennial Pavilion in the Columbus Commons.
Event Website >> (http://www.columbussymphony.com/events/series/profile.dT/popcorn-pops)

