** Garden Chefs Franklin Park Conservatory
------------------------------------------------------------

July 5th

Children participate in workshops that focus on gardening, cooking, and healthy living activities including bird watching, scavenger hunts, cooking from the garden and more. Each interactive workshop includes a take home portion.

