** The Glorious Fourth Ohio Village
------------------------------------------------------------

July 4th

Enjoy a leisurely afternoon of old-fashioned family activities to celebrate the nation's independence at this re-created 19th-century village, including a Grand Procession, patriotic speeches, Muffins base ball, a concert by the Ohio Village Singers and a community dance. Hungry? Plan to enter our pie-eating contests, but be sure to save room for ice cream!

